            "text": "<p>To keep your swimwear happy and healthy, please follow our general care guidelines:</p><ul><li>hand-wash separately in cool water so the colours do not bleed. </li><li>Please avoid traditional washers and abrasive materials like velcro and bleach.  </li><li>Do not leave wet swimsuit in a bag. </li><li>Air dry in a shady spot.</li></ul>",
