            "section_class": "section_class",
            "page": "",
            "title": "Shipping, Returns & Warranty",
            "text": "<p><strong>SHIPPING</strong></p><p>Worldwide<strong> </strong>shipping from Bali & Australia. Free EXPRESS Shipping for orders $250+ AUD.</p><p>International Express Shipping will be sent via DHL and will arrive in 2 - 4 days once dispatched.</p><p>Domestic Indonesian & Australian orders will be sent express and arrive in 1 - 3 days.</p><p>See our Returns policy <a href=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\">here.</a></p><p>Please read more of our Shipping Policy <a href=\"/policies/shipping-policy\" title=\"Shipping Policy\">here.</a></p><p><strong>RETURNS/EXCHANGES</strong></p><p>We accept exchanges or returns for change of mind for a credit note, on full price items only, and as long as it is processed within within 30 days from the date the item was dispatched.</p><p>Sale items cannot be exchanged or refunded.</p><p>Please follow instructions on our  <a href=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\" title=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\">Returns </a>page.</p><p><strong>WARRANTY</strong></p><p>We stand by the quality of our swimsuits, they are tailor made with high quality Italian fabric. </p><p>We offer a 12 month warranty from date of purchase, shall the make, material or hardware malfunction.</p><p>Read more about our warranty <a href=\"/pages/warranty\" title=\"Warranty\">here.</a></p>",
            "default_open_accordion": false
          }
        },
