      "blocks": {
        "accordion_pane_m6HGAA": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does the Snow white colour transparent when wet?",
            "content": "<p>We line all our snow white surf suits with a beige econyl sustainable fabric, to prevent them from becoming transparent.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_zwBQPA": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do your surf suits have built in support?",
            "content": "<p>Our one piece surf suits do not have built in support.  They are double lined and are a firm cut, designed to hold you in.  We have customers from a AA-D that are happy with the support with our surf suits.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_cYX4Eg": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "do these surfsuits have adjustable coverage?",
            "content": "<p>You can adjust the fit of each surf suit by hitching the leg high up on your hip, which gives you brief coverage.  Or pull it down on your hip for more coverage.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_Py7J3k": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Which one piece suit provides the most UPF?",
            "content": "<p>If UPF protection is important to you, opt for the darker colours. The Sulawesi in Midnight provides the most UPF block out, due to the dark colour of the fabric and long sleeves.  </p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_ArMU9p": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is the fit like on the one piece surf suits?",
            "content": "<p>All our one piece surf suits are designed to be like shape wear and hold you in.  If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up and if buying the midnight go up two sizes, as the black colour doesn't have as much stretch due to the dying process.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
